# Astro Component Conventions

- Components read directly from the imported `siteConfig` object — keep logic minimal
- Use `.astro` files only (no React/Vue/etc)
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Use Tabler Icons for any new icons

## When Modifying Components

1. Read the existing component structure first
2. Maintain consistency with other components in `src/components/`
3. Test with different config variations (empty data, full data)
4. Don't edit component files for content changes — change `src/config.ts` instead
